<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 13:18:53 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>与特朗普相关的世界自由组织起诉孙宇晨诽谤</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-04/trump-linked-world-liberty-sues-justin-sun-for-defamation</link><description>世界自由金融公司表示，正在以诽谤罪起诉贾斯汀·孙(Justin Sun)，指责这位亿万富翁加密货币企业家在上个月对特朗普相关项目提起诉讼后，针对该项目发起了协调一致的媒体宣传活动。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iAw0svHpP.xU/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 13:08:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-04/trump-linked-world-liberty-sues-justin-sun-for-defamation</guid></item><item><title>随着股市上涨，比特币自 1 月份以来首次突破 80,000 美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-04/bitcoin-btc-tops-80-000-for-three-month-high-as-asian-stocks-rise</link><description>由于看涨情绪提振风险资产，比特币自 1 月份以来首次升至 80,000 美元以上，亚洲股市上涨，美国科技股期货有望进一步上涨。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iw.jWHIx1AUg/v2/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 02:58:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-04/bitcoin-btc-tops-80-000-for-three-month-high-as-asian-stocks-rise</guid></item></channel></rss>